30#define SMU__NUM_SCLK_DPM_STATE 8
31#define SMU__NUM_MCLK_DPM_LEVELS 6
32#define SMU__NUM_LCLK_DPM_LEVELS 8
33#define SMU__NUM_PCIE_DPM_LEVELS 8

36#define CISLANDS_MAX_HARDWARE_POWERLEVELS 2
37
38#define CISLANDS_UNUSED_GPIO_PIN 0x7F
39
40struct ci_pl {
41 u32 mclk;
42 u32 sclk;
43 enum radeon_pcie_gen pcie_gen;
44 u16 pcie_lane;
45};
46
47struct ci_ps {
48 u16 performance_level_count;
49 bool dc_compatible;
50 u32 sclk_t;
51 struct ci_pl performance_levels[CISLANDS_MAX_HARDWARE_POWERLEVELS];
52};
53
54struct ci_dpm_level {
55 bool enabled;
56 u32 value;
57 u32 param1;
58};
59
60#define CISLAND_MAX_DEEPSLEEP_DIVIDER_ID 5
61#define MAX_REGULAR_DPM_NUMBER 8
62#define CISLAND_MINIMUM_ENGINE_CLOCK 800
63
64struct ci_single_dpm_table {
65 u32 count;
66 struct ci_dpm_level dpm_levels[MAX_REGULAR_DPM_NUMBER];
67};
68
69struct ci_dpm_table {
70 struct ci_single_dpm_table sclk_table;
71 struct ci_single_dpm_table mclk_table;
72 struct ci_single_dpm_table pcie_speed_table;
73 struct ci_single_dpm_table vddc_table;
74 struct ci_single_dpm_table vddci_table;
75 struct ci_single_dpm_table mvdd_table;
76};
77
78struct ci_mc_reg_entry {
79 u32 mclk_max;
80 u32 mc_data[SMU7_DISCRETE_MC_REGISTER_ARRAY_SIZE];
81};
82
83struct ci_mc_reg_table {
84 u8 last;
85 u8 num_entries;
86 u16 valid_flag;
87 struct ci_mc_reg_entry mc_reg_table_entry[MAX_AC_TIMING_ENTRIES];
88 SMU7_Discrete_MCRegisterAddress mc_reg_address[SMU7_DISCRETE_MC_REGISTER_ARRAY_SIZE];
89};
90
91struct ci_ulv_parm
92{
93 bool supported;
94 u32 cg_ulv_parameter;
95 u32 volt_change_delay;
96 struct ci_pl pl;
97};
98
99#define CISLANDS_MAX_LEAKAGE_COUNT 8
100
101struct ci_leakage_voltage {
102 u16 count;
103 u16 leakage_id[CISLANDS_MAX_LEAKAGE_COUNT];
104 u16 actual_voltage[CISLANDS_MAX_LEAKAGE_COUNT];
105};
106
107struct ci_dpm_level_enable_mask {
108 u32 uvd_dpm_enable_mask;
109 u32 vce_dpm_enable_mask;
110 u32 acp_dpm_enable_mask;
111 u32 samu_dpm_enable_mask;
112 u32 sclk_dpm_enable_mask;
113 u32 mclk_dpm_enable_mask;
114 u32 pcie_dpm_enable_mask;
115};
116
117struct ci_vbios_boot_state
118{
119 u16 mvdd_bootup_value;
120 u16 vddc_bootup_value;
121 u16 vddci_bootup_value;
122 u32 sclk_bootup_value;
123 u32 mclk_bootup_value;
124 u16 pcie_gen_bootup_value;
125 u16 pcie_lane_bootup_value;
126};

128struct ci_clock_registers {
129 u32 cg_spll_func_cntl;
130 u32 cg_spll_func_cntl_2;
131 u32 cg_spll_func_cntl_3;

134 u32 cg_spll_spread_spectrum_2;
135 u32 dll_cntl;
136 u32 mclk_pwrmgt_cntl;
137 u32 mpll_ad_func_cntl;
138 u32 mpll_dq_func_cntl;
139 u32 mpll_func_cntl;
140 u32 mpll_func_cntl_1;
141 u32 mpll_func_cntl_2;
142 u32 mpll_ss1;
143 u32 mpll_ss2;
144};

157enum ci_pt_config_reg_type {
158 CISLANDS_CONFIGREG_MMR = 0,
159 CISLANDS_CONFIGREG_SMC_IND,
160 CISLANDS_CONFIGREG_DIDT_IND,
161 CISLANDS_CONFIGREG_CACHE,
162 CISLANDS_CONFIGREG_MAX
163};

165#define POWERCONTAINMENT_FEATURE_BAPM 0x00000001
166#define POWERCONTAINMENT_FEATURE_TDCLimit 0x00000002
167#define POWERCONTAINMENT_FEATURE_PkgPwrLimit 0x00000004

169struct ci_pt_config_reg {
170 u32 offset;
171 u32 mask;
172 u32 shift;
173 u32 value;
174 enum ci_pt_config_reg_type type;
175};

177struct ci_pt_defaults {
178 u8 svi_load_line_en;
179 u8 svi_load_line_vddc;

183 u8 dte_ambient_temp_base;
184 u32 display_cac;
185 u32 bapm_temp_gradient;
186 u16 bapmti_r[SMU7_DTE_ITERATIONS * SMU7_DTE_SOURCES * SMU7_DTE_SINKS];
187 u16 bapmti_rc[SMU7_DTE_ITERATIONS * SMU7_DTE_SOURCES * SMU7_DTE_SINKS];
188};

195struct ci_power_info {
196 struct ci_dpm_table dpm_table;
197 u32 voltage_control;
198 u32 mvdd_control;
199 u32 vddci_control;
200 u32 active_auto_throttle_sources;
201 struct ci_clock_registers clock_registers;
202 u16 acpi_vddc;
203 u16 acpi_vddci;
204 enum radeon_pcie_gen force_pcie_gen;
205 enum radeon_pcie_gen acpi_pcie_gen;
206 struct ci_leakage_voltage vddc_leakage;
207 struct ci_leakage_voltage vddci_leakage;
208 u16 max_vddc_in_pp_table;
209 u16 min_vddc_in_pp_table;
210 u16 max_vddci_in_pp_table;
211 u16 min_vddci_in_pp_table;
212 u32 mclk_strobe_mode_threshold;
213 u32 mclk_stutter_mode_threshold;
214 u32 mclk_edc_enable_threshold;
215 u32 mclk_edc_wr_enable_threshold;
216 struct ci_vbios_boot_state vbios_boot_state;
217 /* smc offsets */
218 u32 sram_end;
219 u32 dpm_table_start;
220 u32 soft_regs_start;
221 u32 mc_reg_table_start;
222 u32 fan_table_start;
223 u32 arb_table_start;
224 /* smc tables */
225 SMU7_Discrete_DpmTable smc_state_table;
226 SMU7_Discrete_MCRegisters smc_mc_reg_table;
227 SMU7_Discrete_PmFuses smc_powertune_table;
228 /* other stuff */
229 struct ci_mc_reg_table mc_reg_table;
230 struct atom_voltage_table vddc_voltage_table;
231 struct atom_voltage_table vddci_voltage_table;
232 struct atom_voltage_table mvdd_voltage_table;
233 struct ci_ulv_parm ulv;
234 u32 power_containment_features;
235 const struct ci_pt_defaults *powertune_defaults;
236 u32 dte_tj_offset;
237 bool vddc_phase_shed_control;
238 struct ci_thermal_temperature_setting thermal_temp_setting;
239 struct ci_dpm_level_enable_mask dpm_level_enable_mask;
240 u32 need_update_smu7_dpm_table;
241 u32 sclk_dpm_key_disabled;
242 u32 mclk_dpm_key_disabled;
243 u32 pcie_dpm_key_disabled;
244 u32 thermal_sclk_dpm_enabled;
245 struct ci_pcie_perf_range pcie_gen_performance;
246 struct ci_pcie_perf_range pcie_lane_performance;
247 struct ci_pcie_perf_range pcie_gen_powersaving;
248 struct ci_pcie_perf_range pcie_lane_powersaving;
249 u32 activity_target[SMU7_MAX_LEVELS_GRAPHICS];
250 u32 mclk_activity_target;
251 u32 low_sclk_interrupt_t;
252 u32 last_mclk_dpm_enable_mask;
253 u32 sys_pcie_mask;
254 /* caps */
255 bool caps_power_containment;
256 bool caps_cac;
257 bool caps_sq_ramping;
258 bool caps_db_ramping;
259 bool caps_td_ramping;
260 bool caps_tcp_ramping;
261 bool caps_fps;
262 bool caps_sclk_ds;
263 bool caps_sclk_ss_support;
264 bool caps_mclk_ss_support;
265 bool caps_uvd_dpm;
266 bool caps_vce_dpm;
267 bool caps_samu_dpm;
268 bool caps_acp_dpm;
269 bool caps_automatic_dc_transition;
270 bool caps_sclk_throttle_low_notification;
271 bool caps_dynamic_ac_timing;
272 bool caps_od_fuzzy_fan_control_support;
273 /* flags */
274 bool thermal_protection;
275 bool pcie_performance_request;
276 bool dynamic_ss;
277 bool dll_default_on;
278 bool cac_enabled;
279 bool uvd_enabled;
280 bool battery_state;
281 bool pspp_notify_required;
282 bool mem_gddr5;
283 bool enable_bapm_feature;
284 bool enable_tdc_limit_feature;
285 bool enable_pkg_pwr_tracking_feature;
286 bool use_pcie_performance_levels;
287 bool use_pcie_powersaving_levels;
288 bool uvd_power_gated;
289 /* driver states */
290 struct radeon_ps current_rps;
291 struct ci_ps current_ps;
292 struct radeon_ps requested_rps;
293 struct ci_ps requested_ps;
294 /* fan control */
295 bool fan_ctrl_is_in_default_mode;
296 bool fan_is_controlled_by_smc;
297 u32 t_min;
298 u32 fan_ctrl_default_mode;
299};
